ReleaseNote:
# HLAE 2.123.0 (2021-10-26T07:00Z)
* Included AfxHookSource 1.102.0 (2021-10-26T07:00Z).

## AfxHookSource 1.102.0 (2021-10-26T07:00Z)
* Updated mirv_pov: The GOTV mirv_pov lag compensation feature (implemented thanks to ideas and input from https://davidbdurst.com/) is now enabled by default, also entities predicted / local to the POV-player should be detected accurately now (e.g. viewmodel). If you don't like it, you can disable it with `mirv_cfg mirvPov interpCompensateLatencyOff`. The default cl_interp is a good value, if you happen to know the actual value of the player you can try to get even more accurate by setting it with: `mirv_cvar_hack cl_interp <clInterpValueHere>`
